{"tid":2256261,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"太犯規！世新校花「水梨奶」撐爆泳衣　神秘三角洲形狀全曝","createTime":"2020-10-24T08:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T08:32:18.000Z","uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f57a7d51a967ae54951345403736b13284800366","tid":2256261,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"在15歲曾參加過《我猜我猜我猜猜》爆紅的冰淇淋女孩陳葳，因魔鬼的身材，甜美的外型，還有著「世新校花」的封號，日前她在IG上曬出一張穿著黑色深V泳裝，兩顆傲人上圍直接爆開泳裝，引起網友鼻血狂噴。<br />\n<br />\n陳葳疑似是去海水浴場玩水，從照片中可以看出，她手拿救生圈，穿著黑色連身泳衣，深V的設計，讓她渾圓的美胸直接炸出，側邊的裸空設計，更是將零贅肉的腰間給凸顯出來，火辣程度直逼限制級。<br />\n<br />\n不少網友看了陳葳泳照，紛紛底下留言，「太辣了吧」、「好嫵媚的表情」、「已戀愛」、「好身材無法擋」，事實上，陳葳現在除了擔任網路模特兒，還兼做直播主，吸引近30萬粉絲支持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NzpBzH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NzpBzH.jpg&h=e92bbb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFtaw72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFtaw72.jpg&h=5cca9155&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23748381b7a9a8ac7185e8269713849caa1ff177","tid":2256261,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}